{"tid":2117874,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★沙灘人流飆升1倍 泳客埋怨泳灘圍封，向救生員發洩。","createTime":"2020-07-21T06:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T07:31:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cc51ddf99c76105ce9af7f7ad9788b5a395a3793","tid":2117874,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:40:37.000Z","msg":"香港新冠肺炎個案急增，康文署日前已關閉轄下泳灘，惟大批市民繼續湧到沙灘暢泳，懶理感染風險。港九拯溺員工會發言人胡啟榮今早(21日)在電台節目表示，近日較大的泳灘如清水灣、淺水灣、黃金泳灘等，人流比去年同期起碼多30%至1倍，甚至有泳客埋怨更衣室關閉水喉，向救生員發洩。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，即使泳灘的入口已圍封，廣播亦有提示場地已關閉，但不少泳客仍繼續闖入，由於救生員無執法權故難以阻止。他又批評，工會雖有向康文署反映，但署方只着救生員加強巡查，及呼籲市民在疫情下要盡量忍耐，避免到沙灘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200721/bkn-20200721114640575-0721_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200721%2Fbkn-20200721114640575-0721_00822_001.html&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhPzDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=1992d9fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200721/bkn-20200721114640575-0721_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9d84ba9c9786c637982d2a16b208a08612b0a311","tid":2117874,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:40:51.000Z","msg":"向救生員發洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853b9574f542ab7339565f589e8e4c1a0fb45bab","tid":2117874,"uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200721/photo/bkn-20200721114640575-0721_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200721125245\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200721%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200721114640575-0721_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200721125245&h=b8b68e39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e952